This is a fork of the original implementation of the Mapper algorithm in Python, by Daniel Müllner and Aravindakshan Babu.

For details see below:


---------------------
    Python Mapper
---------------------

Copyright 2011–2015 by the authors:
    Daniel Müllner, http://danifold.net
    Aravindakshan Babu, anounceofpractice@hotmail.com

Python Mapper is an open source tool for exploration, analysis and
visualization of data. It is distributed under the GPLv3 license. See the
project home page

    http://danifold.net/mapper

for more information, including installation instructions and documentation.
